    "Holistic Examination of GPT Applications in Tourism:",
    "The research furnishes a comprehensive exploration of various GPT applications in the tourism sector, not limited to customer interaction and engagement but also extending to operational processes, service customization, and multilingual communication.",
    "These insights could serve as a guide for tourism practitioners, technologists, and strategists, as they navigate through the myriad of possibilities brought forth by GPT technologies.",
    "The identification and meticulous analysis of barriers hindering the adoption of GPT technologies render a pragmatic viewpoint, allowing stakeholders to anticipate challenges and formulate mitigation strategies.",
    "Through delineating these barriers, this research also offers strategic insights that could inform the development of tools and frameworks to navigate through these impediments effectively."
